<tt>Mon Dec 16 11:58:46 US/Eastern 1996
</tt><p>
My thoughts on the Vietnam war are from a childs point of view.  I feel sorrow when I read these stories and comments.  I feel confused when I think about all of the fighting.  And I feel hurt when I think that no one could keep peace for the childrens sakes.  And I hate the fact that some people had to face the fact that they wouldn't see there loved ones ever again.  The only happiness that I feel is the happiness of loved ones finally coming home.  Maybe there won't ever be a need for me to feel all of these mixed emotions again.  I hope there is not, because when I do, it is always war related.
